description:
Super Spin Digital and Monstercat have picked a selection of 10 incredible tracks for our first DLC. This pack contains a collection of nostalgic beats, popular Monstercat classics and some hidden gems which we think suit the gameplay of Spin Rhythm XD perfectly. 

TRACK LIST

Cheat Codes - Nitro Fun
CRAZY - Tokyo Machine
Into the Light - Notaker, Karra
Shut My Mouth - Koven
THE DROP - Gammer
Blue Shadows - Xilent
Overkill - RIOT
U Got Me - Bossfight
How We Win - FWLR
It's All Over - Shockone

SKINS

Monstercat wheel skin
Monstercat menu palette
"Hi-Fi" track edge skin
"Veridian" track edge colour
name: Spin Rhythm XD Monstercat DLC
